import {createAction} from '@reduxjs/toolkit'
import {AuthTypes} from "../reducers/authReducer"

export const FETCH_TOKEN = 'FETCH_TOKEN'
export const FETCH_TOKEN_BEGIN = 'FETCH_TOKEN_BEGIN'
export const FETCH_TOKEN_SUCCESS = 'FETCH_TOKEN_SUCCESS'
export const FETCH_TOKEN_FAILURE = 'FETCH_TOKEN_FAILURE'
export const SET_IS_AUTH = 'SET_IS_AUTH'

export const authActions = {
    fetchTokenBegin: createAction('token/beginFetch'),
    fetchTokenSuccess: createAction('token/fetchSuccess'),
    fetchTokenFailure: createAction('token/fetchFailure')
};
